### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  Tasero — Rates API
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

@apiKey={{$dotenv TEST_API_KEY}}

### Health check / Get BCV exchange rates
# Requires API key with "read:rates" scope
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rates/bcv
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Get BCV rates — without auth (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rates/bcv

### Get BCV rates — invalid API key (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rates/bcv
Authorization: Bearer sk_tas_invalid_key_here

